body:
This mod improves the ocean and makes resource gathering, building and progressing in the game possible without touching land. This mod now contains this:

Wood types: Coral oriented, more types of trees;
Tubewood: blue wood, tube corals; Small Tree, Double Tree, Mega Tree (2x2, Tall);
Firewood: red-orange wood, fire corals, corals around the trees, magma blocks around the tree; Small Double Tree with sea pickles around it (Sea Lantern on top), Taller 2x2 tree;
Bubblewood: Bubble Coral, wood color similar to bubble corals; Small Tree, 2x2 Tall Tree;
Brainwood: Brain coral color, brain coral, Brain coral ecosystem around it (Brain Corals); Small 90° turn tree, Double 90° Turn Tree;

If you think the ocean is boring, download this mod
Tube Mango fruit next update; a tropical underwater fruit with special properties; a little tree that generates on tubewood trees;

